testMovingOutOfBoundsDown() - Method in class testing.entities.PlayerTester
The player is not supposed to move down when its y position is greater than or equal to 480.
This test makes the player move to down until it stops moving.
Then, test if the y position where it stopped is greater than or equal to 480.
testMovingOutOfBoundsLeft() - Method in class testing.entities.PlayerTester
The player is not supposed to move left when its x position is lesser than or equal to 25.
This test makes the player move to the left until it stops moving.
Then, test if the x position where it stopped is lesser than or equal to 25.
testMovingOutOfBoundsRigh() - Method in class testing.entities.PlayerTester
The player is not supposed to move right when its x position is greater than or equal to 340.
This test makes the player move to the right until it stops moving.
Then, test if the x position where it stopped is greater than or equal to 340.
testMovingOutOfBoundsUp() - Method in class testing.entities.PlayerTester
The player is not supposed to move up when its position is lesser than or equal to 80.
This test makes the player move to up until it stops moving.
